snippet.title: The Survivalists - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The Survivalists is available now: https://nintendo.com/games/detail/the-survivalists-switch/
The Survivalists is an adventure-filled, procedurally generated survival game set in The Escapists universe. Play alone or with up to three friends in online co-op to explore fantastical islands. Are you ready to explore, build and craft in The Survivalists? Available now on Nintendo Switch 🐵

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
